A perl script for generating seminar bingo cards, uses pdflatex.

1. Populate "words.txt" with the words and phrases you want to use,
2. Generate a pdf file containing cards using seminar_bingo.pl
3. Print the cards
4. Hand the cards to members of the audience
5. The first member to get an entire row, column or main-diagonal from
their card of terms/phrases used by the speaker(s), either verbally or
on a slide must shout "Bingo!"
6. The award is a free paper/grant review from each of the other
participants or other pre-arranged reward


